one minute and two seconds.

27
00:02:47,600 --> 00:02:50,956
Look, Tamotsu, I really
envy your friend Gunma.

28
00:02:51,480 --> 00:02:53,357
This is a good thing?

29
00:02:53,600 --> 00:02:56,353
Yes, because my mechanics
aren't good enough.

30
